''XHTML 2.0 suggestion: <caption> for <object>, <attribution> for <blockquote> from Robin Lionheart on 2003-05-10 (www-html@@w3.org from May 2003)'' <http://lists.w3.org/Archives/Public/www-html/2003May/0039.html>

歴史は繰り返す。
