''XHTML2.0 expanding blockquote with bibliography from Lorenzo De Tomasi on 2002-08-09 (www-html@@w3.org from August 2002)'' <http://lists.w3.org/Archives/Public/www-html/2002Aug/0092.html>

同じく XHTML 2 への [CODE(XMLe)[bibliography]] 要素型の提案。

([[名無しさん]])

